com.clarionmedia.infinitum.rest
Interface Deserializer<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
JsonDeserializer, XmlDeserializer
public interface Deserializer<T>

A Deserializer is used to convert web service responses into domain objects. Web service responses are typically sent back as JSON or XML. For the former, see the implementation JsonDeserializer, and the latter, XmlDeserializer.

Version:
1.0 05/21/12
Author:
Tyler Treat
